                        "en": {"text": "<p>I'm a Software Engineer with 4+ years of experience in designing and building scalable and data-driven solutions in the robotics and video streaming industry</b>. My expertise in <b>Python, SQL and Cloud technologies</b> enables me to tackle complex problems across various domains.</p><p>I enjoy solving technical challenges and optimizing systems to deliver high-performance results.</p><p>Looking forward to working <b>together!</b>" },                         
